TI  - A novel feature-oriented quality of anything (QoX) framework for end-to-end robotic services in 6G networks
AU  - Varvara Mineeva
AU  - Abdelhamied A. Ateya
AU  - Artem Volkov
AU  - Ammar Muthanna
AU  - Andrey Koucheryavy
AU  - Samia A. Chelloug
AU  - Ahmed A. Abd El-Latif
